WEBVTT

00:00:35.970 --> 00:00:38.770
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.770 --> 00:00:41.270
=Episode 15=

00:00:42.083 --> 00:00:43.625
You are Feng Fuliu.

00:00:46.833 --> 00:00:48.458
Last night, while I was unconscious,

00:00:48.916 --> 00:00:51.708
you used the chaos to carry me
back to Chong'er Pavilion.

00:00:53.125 --> 00:00:56.083
Then you became Chang Beiming again
to confuse everyone.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:00:57.875
Go on.

00:00:58.958 --> 00:00:59.750
Keep making things up.

00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:02.875
I have a witness.

00:01:06.333 --> 00:01:06.666
Bingfan.

00:01:07.583 --> 00:01:08.500
Are you hurt?

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:09.041
Guan.

00:01:09.333 --> 00:01:10.625
I'm hurt!

00:01:11.166 --> 00:01:12.875
Did Chang Beiming leave
Chong'er Pavilion last night?

00:01:12.875 --> 00:01:13.333
No.

00:01:15.458 --> 00:01:16.708
He never left my sight last night.

00:01:17.083 --> 00:01:17.541
Are you sure?

00:01:18.916 --> 00:01:20.125
You told me to stay with him,

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.458
so I didn’t leave him
for even a second.

00:01:23.041 --> 00:01:23.500
Bingfan,

00:01:23.958 --> 00:01:25.500
around sunset yesterday,

00:01:25.625 --> 00:01:27.333
he was playing cards with Feng Zhihe
and the others.

00:01:27.500 --> 00:01:28.708
They played until nightfall.

00:01:28.833 --> 00:01:30.875
Then he lost badly, got upset,
and went to sleep.

00:01:31.125 --> 00:01:31.666
After that,

00:01:31.666 --> 00:01:33.333
Feng Zhihe and the others
kept making me drink.

00:01:33.458 --> 00:01:34.125
We drank past midnight,

00:01:34.333 --> 00:01:35.041
and I got drunk too.

00:01:38.333 --> 00:01:38.750
Bingfan,

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:40.166
but I swear,

00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:42.583
before that, he definitely never left.

00:01:43.458 --> 00:01:43.833
I swear.

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:49.041
(Last night,)

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:52.041
(I fought Feng Fuliu almost all night.)

00:01:52.500 --> 00:01:54.500
(If Chang Beiming never left,)

00:01:55.708 --> 00:01:57.041
(then he is not Feng Fuliu.)

00:01:59.890 --> 00:02:02.640
(Calm and Unruffled)

00:02:04.708 --> 00:02:06.000
I really didn't mean to hit you.

00:02:06.458 --> 00:02:07.708
Next time, before you attack,

00:02:08.416 --> 00:02:09.916
can you maybe think first?

00:02:10.416 --> 00:02:11.208
I'm sorry.

00:02:12.291 --> 00:02:13.750
But you need to explain

00:02:14.583 --> 00:02:16.666
why you were in my room.

00:02:19.958 --> 00:02:21.208
Last night, I was playing cards.

00:02:22.083 --> 00:02:22.875
My luck was terrible.

00:02:23.416 --> 00:02:24.375
I lost a lot of money.

00:02:25.041 --> 00:02:26.250
Then I kept drinking.

00:02:26.750 --> 00:02:27.291
Too much.

00:02:27.541 --> 00:02:28.458
I drank so much that I got drunk.

00:02:28.458 --> 00:02:29.166
And after I got drunk,

00:02:29.166 --> 00:02:30.541
I passed out right here on the bed.

00:02:30.541 --> 00:02:31.625
Then, while I was asleep.
Knock, knock.

00:02:31.708 --> 00:02:32.750
It was probably around the fourth watch.

00:02:32.750 --> 00:02:33.416
Someone suddenly knocked.

00:02:33.541 --> 00:02:34.625
I jolted awake.

00:02:34.666 --> 00:02:35.125
After I woke up,

00:02:35.125 --> 00:02:36.708
it was pitch dark, so I grabbed a lamp.

00:02:37.125 --> 00:02:38.041
I took the lamp

00:02:38.041 --> 00:02:40.041
and walked over like this.

00:02:40.041 --> 00:02:42.166
I opened the door. No one was there.

00:02:42.250 --> 00:02:42.875
Then I looked down,

00:02:43.083 --> 00:02:43.541
and there you were.

00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:44.125
Right there.

00:02:44.250 --> 00:02:45.833
So I brought the lamp over
and picked you up.

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:47.250
The handcuffs were here.

00:02:47.291 --> 00:02:48.166
So I picked those up too.

00:02:48.166 --> 00:02:48.875
Then I carried you inside.

00:02:48.875 --> 00:02:49.458
Like this.

00:02:49.458 --> 00:02:50.958
Then I shut the door behind me.

00:02:51.083 --> 00:02:52.541
After that, I kept carrying you.

00:02:52.666 --> 00:02:54.916
Honestly, it was hard.
Have you been eating more lately?

00:02:54.916 --> 00:02:55.958
You were heavy. Really heavy.

00:02:56.208 --> 00:02:57.250
You really have been eating more.

00:02:57.250 --> 00:02:58.458
Anyway, I carried you,

00:02:58.708 --> 00:03:00.333
with great effort, and then

00:03:00.333 --> 00:03:01.833
I put you down on this bed.

00:03:01.958 --> 00:03:03.041
Then I took care of you.

00:03:06.250 --> 00:03:07.000
That's all?

00:03:14.875 --> 00:03:16.416
You searched my robe for the amulet?

00:03:21.583 --> 00:03:21.791
You...

00:03:22.083 --> 00:03:24.625
Why did you hit me again?

00:03:27.333 --> 00:03:29.666
You were holding it in your hand.

00:03:38.083 --> 00:03:40.166
How did they become a matching pair?

00:03:41.166 --> 00:03:42.916
How are there two of them?

00:03:46.458 --> 00:03:47.208
I'm sorry.

00:03:48.875 --> 00:03:49.875
I acted rashly again.

00:03:59.208 --> 00:04:01.458
The master who saved you as a child

00:04:04.291 --> 00:04:05.458
was Feng Fuliu.

00:04:11.458 --> 00:04:12.208
Really?

00:04:17.750 --> 00:04:18.791
Bingfan. Young Master Chang.

00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:20.291
Something terrible happened.

00:04:22.708 --> 00:04:23.875
The Dragon-Phoenix Jade was stolen,

00:04:24.250 --> 00:04:25.208
and Mr. Lu
was afraid of taking the blame.

00:04:25.458 --> 00:04:26.125
So he pushed

00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:27.541
all the responsibility onto Hua
and Xintian.

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:29.375
I had to fetch the Commander overnight

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:30.375
to keep things under control.

00:04:31.291 --> 00:04:31.875
But now,

00:04:32.500 --> 00:04:33.416
Hua and Xintian

00:04:33.750 --> 00:04:34.625
have been ordered imprisoned.

00:04:35.208 --> 00:04:35.875
How could this happen?

00:04:36.250 --> 00:04:37.000
Of course it did.

00:04:37.708 --> 00:04:38.500
A treasure was stolen

00:04:38.625 --> 00:04:40.750
from the princess's manor.

00:04:41.208 --> 00:04:43.541
They need scapegoats to close the case.

00:04:44.416 --> 00:04:45.041
This is outrageous.

00:04:45.583 --> 00:04:47.000
I will go argue with your Commander.

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.041
What rank are you?

00:04:48.416 --> 00:04:49.708
You want to argue with the Commander?

00:04:50.541 --> 00:04:51.083
Besides,

00:04:51.791 --> 00:04:52.916
are you even with the Northern Bureau?

00:04:54.541 --> 00:04:55.041
No.

00:04:55.791 --> 00:04:56.208
I will go.

00:04:56.291 --> 00:04:56.666
Bingfan.

00:04:57.625 --> 00:04:58.750
This is too serious.

00:04:59.208 --> 00:04:59.958
We need a proper plan.

00:05:00.416 --> 00:05:02.041
What I hate most is when people
run out of ideas

00:05:02.041 --> 00:05:03.250
and call it "a proper plan".

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.750
My sisters are suffering.
I can't sit and plan.

00:05:09.208 --> 00:05:10.541
I'm going to see the Commander.

00:05:13.250 --> 00:05:14.791
Bingfan, you are so cool. I support you.

00:05:15.916 --> 00:05:16.750
Cool?

00:05:17.541 --> 00:05:18.375
Childish.

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:29.375
Go. Help her.

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:30.208
My lord.

00:05:31.083 --> 00:05:32.416
How are Hua and Xintian?

00:05:32.750 --> 00:05:34.166
We were only following orders
to catch the thief.

00:05:34.583 --> 00:05:36.083
But Mr. Lu accused us
of conspiring with him.

00:05:36.666 --> 00:05:37.625
We are innocent.

00:05:37.833 --> 00:05:38.625
Please clear our names, my lord.

00:05:40.041 --> 00:05:40.791
Don't worry.

00:05:41.625 --> 00:05:41.958
You...

00:05:42.916 --> 00:05:45.000
Why are you hurt again?

00:05:45.500 --> 00:05:47.125
You're a young woman.

00:05:47.583 --> 00:05:49.166
Why are you always getting hurt?

00:05:49.500 --> 00:05:50.500
With that temper of yours,

00:05:52.708 --> 00:05:54.541
who would like to marry you
in the future?

00:05:55.416 --> 00:05:56.041
My lord.

00:05:56.625 --> 00:05:57.916
I'm worried sick.

00:05:58.125 --> 00:05:59.541
How can you still joke about this?

00:05:59.541 --> 00:06:00.708
There you go, rushing again.

00:06:02.791 --> 00:06:03.166
Calm down.

00:06:04.083 --> 00:06:05.541
Think about last night.

00:06:06.333 --> 00:06:08.208
If Lu Guokai hadn't acted quickly

00:06:08.500 --> 00:06:10.708
and detained Mange and Xintian for now,

00:06:11.166 --> 00:06:13.125
they could have ended up
in another office's hands.

00:06:13.500 --> 00:06:15.416
Then they would have suffered far worse.

00:06:17.083 --> 00:06:18.125
So...

00:06:18.916 --> 00:06:20.416
Mr. Lu was trying to protect them?

00:06:20.833 --> 00:06:23.000
Childish! Painfully Childish!

00:06:25.750 --> 00:06:26.666
A theft

00:06:27.250 --> 00:06:28.166
at the princess's manor.

00:06:28.708 --> 00:06:30.750
Do you know how serious that is?

00:06:31.208 --> 00:06:32.875
Without one or two people
taking the blame,

00:06:33.500 --> 00:06:35.458
how can this case be contained for now?

00:06:38.333 --> 00:06:40.958
Xintian and Mange were not sent
to the Imperial Prison.

00:06:41.500 --> 00:06:42.541
They are resting in the back courtyard.

00:06:43.083 --> 00:06:44.708
This is only a show

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:46.083
for outsiders to see.

00:06:46.750 --> 00:06:47.500
Then can I

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:48.958
go see Xintian and Hua now?

00:06:49.458 --> 00:06:50.000
Why are you

00:06:50.375 --> 00:06:52.333
rushing again?

00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:53.750
Let me finish.

00:06:56.875 --> 00:06:58.000
Feng Fuliu

00:06:58.583 --> 00:07:00.000
caused chaos at the princess's manor

00:07:00.291 --> 00:07:02.875
and stole
the imperial Dragon-Phoenix Jade.

00:07:03.541 --> 00:07:05.000
That is a grave crime.

00:07:05.791 --> 00:07:08.041
I can release them, of course.

00:07:08.458 --> 00:07:09.375
But remember this.

00:07:09.625 --> 00:07:10.666
Within three days,

00:07:10.666 --> 00:07:12.458
you must recover the treasure.

00:07:13.125 --> 00:07:14.583
If you fail,

00:07:15.125 --> 00:07:15.583
then

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:18.958
the three of you will be
the ones convicted.

00:07:20.541 --> 00:07:21.250
Understood.

00:07:22.875 --> 00:07:23.458
Go.

00:07:25.390 --> 00:07:27.166
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)

00:07:27.166 --> 00:07:28.375
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)
No rush.

00:07:36.458 --> 00:07:37.166
Are you all right?

00:07:37.291 --> 00:07:39.166
She didn't make a sound.
Why are you crying?

00:07:39.583 --> 00:07:41.166
It hurts just watching Bingfan.

00:07:41.916 --> 00:07:43.750
Why do you keep risking your life
like this?

00:07:44.041 --> 00:07:45.791
You come back covered in wounds
every time.

00:07:46.375 --> 00:07:47.083
Exactly, Bingfan.

00:07:47.666 --> 00:07:48.791
Next time, take me with you.

00:07:49.208 --> 00:07:49.958
At least I can watch your back.

00:07:49.958 --> 00:07:51.083
You have the nerve to say that?

00:07:51.416 --> 00:07:52.458
I asked you to watch Chang Beiming,

00:07:52.875 --> 00:07:53.666
and you ruined it by drinking.

00:07:55.125 --> 00:07:55.583
Bingfan.

00:07:56.416 --> 00:07:57.333
I didn't mean to.

00:07:58.291 --> 00:08:00.000
Ye Ping's uncle is the Grand Secretary.

00:08:00.250 --> 00:08:01.958
Even my superiors at the Ministry
of Justice show him respect.

00:08:02.375 --> 00:08:03.708
I couldn't embarrass him.

00:08:04.458 --> 00:08:04.791
Let me.

00:08:05.375 --> 00:08:08.041
So, according to Constable Guan,

00:08:08.541 --> 00:08:10.916
Chang Beiming is not Feng Fuliu.

00:08:11.833 --> 00:08:12.250
Constable Guan,

00:08:12.708 --> 00:08:13.375
did you see him clearly?

00:08:13.791 --> 00:08:15.916
Are you sure it was Young Master Chang
on the couch?

00:08:16.541 --> 00:08:17.583
Did you get close and check?

00:08:18.083 --> 00:08:18.958
I didn't go close.

00:08:19.541 --> 00:08:20.666
I only saw his back.

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:21.958
Duoyu.

00:08:22.708 --> 00:08:23.416
What do you mean?

00:08:24.166 --> 00:08:25.083
Are you saying

00:08:25.208 --> 00:08:26.500
Chang Beiming switched places
with someone?

00:08:27.666 --> 00:08:28.416
I'm only asking.

00:08:28.833 --> 00:08:30.125
I'm not sure.

00:08:31.166 --> 00:08:33.250
Our instructor said that
when catching a criminal,

00:08:33.541 --> 00:08:35.166
every case must have a motive.

00:08:35.833 --> 00:08:36.750
Then what motive

00:08:36.750 --> 00:08:38.500
would Young Master Chang
have to pretend to be Feng Fuliu?

00:08:44.333 --> 00:08:44.958
That makes no sense.

00:08:45.458 --> 00:08:46.458
He is so rich.

00:08:46.916 --> 00:08:47.833
Why would he steal?

00:08:48.208 --> 00:08:49.958
Maybe what he steals

00:08:49.958 --> 00:08:52.291
can't be bought with money.

00:08:53.458 --> 00:08:55.833
And he always returns what he steals
after a few days.

00:08:56.083 --> 00:08:57.083
Why would he do that?

00:08:57.500 --> 00:08:58.333
That is the strangest part.

00:08:58.833 --> 00:08:59.625
Why would Feng Fuliu

00:08:59.791 --> 00:09:00.625
take such risks

00:09:00.625 --> 00:09:02.500
to steal imperial gifts?

00:09:19.958 --> 00:09:20.708
(Could it be)

00:09:21.333 --> 00:09:22.666
(he is looking for this?)

00:09:27.250 --> 00:09:29.541
(Could the master who saved me back then
be Feng Fuliu?)

00:09:31.666 --> 00:09:32.416
(Then,)

00:09:33.166 --> 00:09:35.000
(Feng Fuliu can't be Chang Beiming.)

00:09:35.708 --> 00:09:38.375
(Chang Beiming is not
as old as a middle-aged man.)

00:09:43.208 --> 00:09:43.958
Wait.

00:09:44.458 --> 00:09:45.666
How old is Chang Beiming?

00:09:46.416 --> 00:09:47.250
I don't know.

00:09:48.458 --> 00:09:49.833
What if he just looks young?

00:10:46.291 --> 00:10:47.625
The courtyard is not large,

00:10:48.166 --> 00:10:48.958
but it is elegant.

00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:50.416
That means

00:10:50.875 --> 00:10:51.833
the owner has good taste.

00:10:52.375 --> 00:10:53.250
You dared to come?

00:10:54.041 --> 00:10:55.125
How's your leg?

00:10:56.833 --> 00:10:57.583
Hua! Xintian!

00:10:58.041 --> 00:10:58.791
Come catch the thief!

00:11:00.458 --> 00:11:01.166
Stop shouting.

00:11:01.666 --> 00:11:04.458
Everyone in Chong'er Pavilion has been
drugged with Red Dust Reverie.

00:11:05.291 --> 00:11:06.125
But don't worry.

00:11:06.250 --> 00:11:06.916
It was a light dose.

00:11:07.333 --> 00:11:09.416
They will wake up by morning.

00:11:09.958 --> 00:11:10.708
Despicable.

00:11:11.041 --> 00:11:11.541
Despicable?

00:11:12.208 --> 00:11:12.875
I

00:11:14.041 --> 00:11:15.000
just missed you too much.

00:11:19.833 --> 00:11:20.375
Feng Fuliu.

00:11:21.041 --> 00:11:21.875
Let me ask you something.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:23.708
Years ago,

00:11:24.375 --> 00:11:25.833
did you save

00:11:25.833 --> 00:11:27.291
a seventeen-year-old girl
from the Iron-Blooded Three Eagles?

00:11:31.458 --> 00:11:32.458
And if I did?

00:11:36.125 --> 00:11:36.833
What would you do?

00:11:40.291 --> 00:11:41.250
I would thank you.

00:11:41.958 --> 00:11:42.916
But I would still arrest you.

00:11:43.833 --> 00:11:45.000
Take it to Princess Pingyang.

00:11:46.083 --> 00:11:47.125
I don't want anything
to happen to you.

00:12:00.833 --> 00:12:01.708
Chang Beiming.

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:07.250
Chang Beiming.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:09.208
Chang Beiming.

00:12:21.750 --> 00:12:23.666
(Was he drugged
by Red Dust Reverie too?)

00:12:29.125 --> 00:12:30.666
Are you two the same person, or not?

00:12:38.458 --> 00:12:39.125
Finally!

00:12:39.916 --> 00:12:42.333
You've got it!

00:12:44.333 --> 00:12:47.958
This time, we recovered
the Dragon-Phoenix Jade.

00:12:48.208 --> 00:12:51.458
The princess is full of praise
for our female Jinyiwei.

00:12:51.875 --> 00:12:52.416
Good!

00:12:52.750 --> 00:12:53.250
Guokai.

00:12:54.125 --> 00:12:54.666
You've got it!

00:12:57.458 --> 00:12:58.041
Chief Squad Leader Shen.

00:12:58.458 --> 00:12:59.458
There is one thing I don't understand.

00:12:59.583 --> 00:13:01.125
How did you get

00:13:01.625 --> 00:13:03.375
the Dragon-Phoenix Jade back
from Feng Fuliu?

00:13:05.333 --> 00:13:06.416
I didn't take it back.

00:13:06.708 --> 00:13:08.250
Feng Fuliu returned it himself.

00:13:08.250 --> 00:13:09.208
He returned it himself?

00:13:09.666 --> 00:13:10.083
Yes.

00:13:10.625 --> 00:13:12.500
That is how Feng Fuliu usually works.

00:13:12.625 --> 00:13:14.666
After stealing a treasure
and keeping it for a while,

00:13:14.666 --> 00:13:15.625
he returns it on his own.

00:13:16.333 --> 00:13:16.833
But this...

00:13:17.583 --> 00:13:19.333
This was awfully fast.

00:13:19.333 --> 00:13:19.958
Guokai.

00:13:20.333 --> 00:13:22.041
Why worry about that?

00:13:22.416 --> 00:13:24.333
The treasure is back.
That is what matters.

00:13:24.708 --> 00:13:25.541
In this operation,

00:13:25.833 --> 00:13:28.500
you adapted quickly
and stayed calm under pressure.

00:13:28.916 --> 00:13:31.375
Although Feng Fuliu was not captured,

00:13:31.625 --> 00:13:32.000
you

00:13:32.208 --> 00:13:34.625
recovered the Dragon-Phoenix Jade.

00:13:35.041 --> 00:13:36.000
That is no small achievement.

00:13:37.875 --> 00:13:38.916
Therefore, I have decided

00:13:39.291 --> 00:13:42.500
to grant Shen Bingfan the rank of Baihu.

00:13:43.166 --> 00:13:46.125
Hua Mange and Cheng Xintian will
be promoted to Chief Squad Leader.

00:13:48.458 --> 00:13:50.333
My lord, that is far too fast.

00:13:50.541 --> 00:13:50.916
I mean,

00:13:51.666 --> 00:13:54.416
the female Jinyiwei
have no official establishment anyway.

00:13:54.708 --> 00:13:57.083
Even if they are promoted, they
only receive equivalent rank treatment.

00:13:57.416 --> 00:13:57.750
You...

00:14:01.208 --> 00:14:01.875
Open.

00:14:04.458 --> 00:14:04.916
Open your mind.

00:14:05.583 --> 00:14:07.041
Look. They got promoted again.

00:14:07.416 --> 00:14:09.708
- Why?
- Exactly. Why them?

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:18.000
If my parents knew
I now had an official post

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:18.833
and even got promoted,

00:14:19.083 --> 00:14:21.125
they would be too happy to sleep.

00:14:24.250 --> 00:14:26.708
This uniform is narrow on top
and wide below.

00:14:27.166 --> 00:14:28.375
It feels awful to wear.

00:14:28.875 --> 00:14:29.458
Hua.

00:14:29.750 --> 00:14:31.083
That is because your figure is too good.

00:14:31.291 --> 00:14:33.583
That is why the uniform
feels uncomfortable.

00:14:36.375 --> 00:14:37.291
And Bingfan

00:14:37.541 --> 00:14:39.750
looks so heroic in hers.

00:14:41.250 --> 00:14:42.333
Xintian.

00:14:42.583 --> 00:14:45.291
You are getting sweeter by the day.

00:14:46.458 --> 00:14:48.375
But I still like Bingfan more.

00:14:51.958 --> 00:14:53.416
Hua. Bingfan. Xintian.

00:14:56.375 --> 00:14:57.958
All three of you were promoted.

00:14:59.208 --> 00:14:59.875
Duoyu.

00:15:00.458 --> 00:15:02.166
I forgot to ask the Commander

00:15:02.166 --> 00:15:03.041
to reward you for your help.

00:15:05.083 --> 00:15:07.000
I'm only a lowly servant.

00:15:07.458 --> 00:15:08.791
If you asked for a reward for me,

00:15:09.125 --> 00:15:10.541
Commissioner Lu would be displeased.

00:15:11.208 --> 00:15:13.000
Why should I care if he is displeased?

00:15:15.250 --> 00:15:16.708
This uniform is still a little tight.

00:15:16.958 --> 00:15:17.291
Hua.

00:15:17.791 --> 00:15:18.875
Does your uniform not fit?

00:15:19.250 --> 00:15:20.541
Send it to me tonight.
I can alter it for you.

00:15:22.458 --> 00:15:23.166
You...

00:15:24.166 --> 00:15:25.250
You can sew too?

00:15:26.750 --> 00:15:27.208
A little.

00:15:28.375 --> 00:15:31.833
Duoyu, you are full of surprises.

00:15:35.666 --> 00:15:36.333
Duoyu.

00:15:37.041 --> 00:15:38.458
If Feng Fuliu is caught,

00:15:38.458 --> 00:15:39.666
what will happen to him?

00:15:40.041 --> 00:15:40.666
Him?

00:15:41.166 --> 00:15:42.958
He is the second-ranked fugitive
on the Bounty List.

00:15:43.208 --> 00:15:45.625
If he is caught, it will mean death.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:47.291
But he has never hurt anyone.

00:15:47.625 --> 00:15:48.791
And all the treasures

00:15:48.791 --> 00:15:50.000
he stole were returned in full.

00:15:51.416 --> 00:15:53.208
But he did break in and steal.

00:15:53.500 --> 00:15:53.958
And

00:15:54.291 --> 00:15:56.625
his targets were imperial relatives,
nobles, and officials.

00:15:57.250 --> 00:16:00.250
That is open defiance of the law
and contempt for imperial authority.

00:16:00.625 --> 00:16:01.583
That alone

00:16:02.041 --> 00:16:03.458
is enough to condemn him to death.

00:16:22.791 --> 00:16:23.708
Umbrellas!

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:25.041
Check it out!

00:16:25.041 --> 00:16:27.350
(Northern Bureau)

00:16:28.291 --> 00:16:28.916
Guan.

00:16:30.583 --> 00:16:31.166
Bingfan.

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:34.000
Congratulations on becoming Baihu.

00:16:34.750 --> 00:16:35.208
Thank you.

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:37.416
Are you free tonight?

00:16:38.333 --> 00:16:39.458
Are you asking me to dinner again?

00:16:43.166 --> 00:16:44.958
I mainly want to celebrate with you.

00:16:46.375 --> 00:16:46.833
All right.

00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:49.500
I have something to say to you too.

00:16:59.458 --> 00:17:00.583
Why are we here again?

00:17:03.208 --> 00:17:04.583
Because I never finished
what I wanted to say last time.

00:17:05.458 --> 00:17:06.000
Guan.

00:17:06.541 --> 00:17:07.500
You are a straightforward man.

00:17:07.708 --> 00:17:09.458
So I will be direct too.

00:17:13.333 --> 00:17:14.583
I know how you feel about me.

00:17:16.291 --> 00:17:17.375
But I once swore

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:19.500
that until I catch Leng Xin,

00:17:20.666 --> 00:17:22.208
I will not think about

00:17:22.416 --> 00:17:23.666
love or romance.

00:17:25.625 --> 00:17:26.208
That is fine.

00:17:26.750 --> 00:17:27.333
I can wait.

00:17:29.208 --> 00:17:31.166
If it takes one year,
I will wait one year.

00:17:31.458 --> 00:17:33.083
If it takes ten years,
I will wait ten years.

00:17:33.958 --> 00:17:35.833
Even if it takes a lifetime,
I can wait.

00:17:36.208 --> 00:17:38.708
No. That is not what I mean.

00:17:41.375 --> 00:17:42.375
Let me put it this way.

00:17:43.458 --> 00:17:45.083
Even if Leng Xin is caught,

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:46.041
we...

00:17:46.541 --> 00:17:47.208
We still cannot be together.

00:17:48.208 --> 00:17:48.916
Why?

00:17:49.125 --> 00:17:50.125
There is no reason.

00:17:50.541 --> 00:17:51.250
It is just impossible.

00:17:52.708 --> 00:17:53.583
I don't believe that.

00:17:53.958 --> 00:17:55.041
There must be a reason.

00:17:59.208 --> 00:18:00.000
I...

00:18:00.708 --> 00:18:02.166
I'm not interested in men right now.

00:18:04.041 --> 00:18:05.916
Anyway, don't waste your time on me.

00:18:06.416 --> 00:18:07.875
Hua told me to make things clear,

00:18:08.208 --> 00:18:08.875
so I would not hold you back.

00:18:09.208 --> 00:18:10.083
Now I have said what I needed to say.

00:18:10.458 --> 00:18:10.791
So,

00:18:10.916 --> 00:18:11.625
that is all.

00:18:39.140 --> 00:18:42.310
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:42.680 --> 00:18:46.060
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:46.310 --> 00:18:49.310
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:49.310 --> 00:18:52.720
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:53.810 --> 00:18:57.020
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:18:57.430 --> 00:19:00.770
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:01.350 --> 00:19:03.560
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:03.560 --> 00:19:07.600
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:11.470
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:11.470 --> 00:19:15.220
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.430
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:17.430 --> 00:19:21.970
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:22.270 --> 00:19:23.770
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:23.770 --> 00:19:26.140
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:26.140 --> 00:19:30.020
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:30.020 --> 00:19:32.350
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:32.350 --> 00:19:37.350
♪And run toward this vast life♪